channel.title: Deobing the latest Runescape (i'm a newb, sorry)
channel.description:
As far as deobing goes I mean.
Help me understand this deobing procedure. Is it where you download the REAL RS files from Jagex somehow, or something entirely different?
If the former, is it possible to deob and obtain the newest RS client? (the one just released with new prayers and improved dragon axe) If the latter, please direct me to where I can find an explanation.
Thanks :cool:
